{"tid":1891794,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"疫情似乎無法受控 可能會變得似流感咁樣大流行","createTime":"2020-02-22T05:58:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-22T10:29:48.000Z","uid":30791,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"44bb9099e18471b66a0b60a1a5c761a34235677d","tid":1891794,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T05:58:38.000Z","msg":"疫苗至少要一兩年時間先會有<br />\n雖然夏天病毒傳染能力應該會下降<br />\n但係染病人數太多<br />\n中共又唔會比工廠商業無限期停頓<br />\n先進國家尚且無法控制<br />\n窮困國家情況將會更差<br />\n長此下去 每個人既中招機率其實會變得越黎越大<br />\n即係大家要有心理準備 係疫苗面世之前都要持續咁抗疫"},{"pid":"15d3497b1c3e0dfb2ef7c9661be01936466f21ec","tid":1891794,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T06:00:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中國官方最新數據指出 武漢肺炎為廢老殺手<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1886478\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1886478</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n研究指出長期病患者死亡率較正常人高<br />\n如果無可避免高機率患病<br />\n咁樣要避免染病死亡 就要保持身體健康 減少自己患上長期病機會"},{"pid":"7838fdda89f44d7a37e63e37333b187a321eb494","tid":1891794,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T06:01:32.000Z","msg":"抗疫要保持身體健康 網上建議包括<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ePcnpS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ePcnpS</a>"},{"pid":"5da20f459c04af28b7e8964c7444ffcd5fb638bd","tid":1891794,"uid":275238,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T06:02:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UYU2h3S.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUYU2h3S.jpg&h=a2f2bfc6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"70414a0605f8319b1c80504c513caee617b98480","tid":1891794,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T06:08:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b80ff1b137b16fff9de70e20f1bb765a07f03e2d","tid":1891794,"uid":205462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T06:11:18.000Z","msg